title: Newbie
description: It might be time for a Husky history lesson. Don't worry, there are lots of die-hards in Seattle who will be happy to reminisce about the glory days.

title: Coug fan in training
description: You clearly know enough to pass as a true fan, but you've got some learning to do.

title: Seasoned fan
description: There's no question you're a true Coug. You likely have a picture of the Palouse as your desktop screensaver, a Mike Leach "swing your sword" banner on your wall and a half-eaten tin of Cougar Gold Cheese sitting in your room.

title: True die-hard
description: Crimson runs deep in your veins. You should probably be the one quizzing us.
